;Group 4 : full load, 3rd gear, 3000 rpm
;4,1:2850-3150rpm
;4,2:Spec start of inj. 16-22.5 ° BTDC
;4,3:Spec inj duration 19-22.5 ° Ck.
;4,4:Synchro angle -3..+3 °Ck.

5,0,Starting conditions
