L00,Engine Control Unit (J248) Coding-2
L01,11463 = Cruise Control System (CCS) Activation
;13647 = Adaptive Cruise Control (ACC) Activation
L02,16167 = Cruise Control System (CCS) Deactivation
L03,12233 = Adaptation Enabling
L04, 
L05,IMMOBILIZER:
L06,Prior to adapting a new USED Engine Control Unit the
L07,Vehicle specific PIN/SKC (IMMO-Login) of the new USED
L08,Engine Control Unit has to be used to enable the adaptation.
L09,You'll find the PIN/SKC on the Key Tag of the additional
L10,Key (of the Donor Car) or you can acquire it through your
L11,responsible Distribution Center or Importer.
